Class Customizables

java.lang.Object
Customizables
All Implemented Interfaces:
Purchaseable
public class Customizables extends Object implements Purchaseable
The Customizables class represents the customizable objects which are predefined that can be customized and sold in the Vending Machine. This class also implements the interface Purchaseable.
